:spinning_rainbow_sheep:  Build Challenge :spinning_rainbow_sheep: 
Looking at the *sheer* quality of entries from the last challenge, we are kicking off another build challenge. Now that we have loads of new dye color options available, let's have some fun! What *wool*d a blissful looking wool house look like? Create your interpretation of a blissful house using only wool as the main component to your housing structure! This challenge is definitely not for the *sheep*ish! 

:build_plate: Sheer Bliss Challenge - March 2nd to March 16th

📄 Guidelines:
:earth: Must be built in Minecraft Earth
:loading: This should be a brand new build and not be something that you've already built
:grass_block:  Build plate size will not matter & won't be a factor in judging
:mining: Feel free to ask for advice pertaining to your build in #sheer-bliss-challenge
:mob_of_me: All work must be done by one individual
:fast_parrot: Remember, this is for fun only
📌If it's a submission picture, please feel free to ask a moderator to pin it.
:sign: Winning submissions may be used in social media posts

Get started with your ✂️
